Dataset Information- This project uses a Twitter Sentiment Analysis dataset, publicly accessible via Google Drive.

File Name:`twitter_sentiment_data.csv`  
Download Link: Click here to access the dataset- (https://drive.google.com/file/d/1TP-z2Avk40LjkWflzo2bYFDJ8V0WSWtn/view?usp=sharing)

Dataset Description:
The dataset includes the following fields:
- `tweet_id` – Unique tweet ID
- `text` – Tweet content
- `created_at` – Timestamp of the tweet
- `user_location` – Location (if available)
- `sentiment` – Label: Positive, Negative, or Neutral

How to Use:
1. Download the dataset from the link above.
2. Save it in your local project folder under `/data`.
3. Load it in your notebook using:

python
import pandas as pd
df = pd.read_csv("data/twitter_sentiment_data.csv")

